index = Index(['field1', 'field2'], 'simple_field_double_index', 'simple_id')
model = SimpleIndexInterface()
index.put(model)
result = Database.get().get(

    , model._id)
self.assertEqual(result['field1'], 'field1')
self.assertEqual(result['field2'], 'field2')
